**Inertia pages vs. controllers:** Committed pages today cover `dashboard`, `onboarding`, `welcome`, `admin/*`, `auth/*`, `billing/index`, `kosmo/index`, `patients/*`, and `settings/*`. Controllers also render many **`workspace/*`**, **`appointments/*`**, **`schedule/*`**, **`invoices/*`**, **`messages/*`**, and **`portal/*`** pages that may not have a matching file under `resources/js/pages/` yet вЂ” align new UI with the exact `Inertia::render('вЂ¦')` string in each action.

Wayfinder generates `resources/js/actions/` during `npm run dev` (directory is gitignored here); never edit generated files by hand.

